<MELItem itemNbr="44-12-02" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-44-12-02.1.2-44-12-02">
<Title>Prerecorded Passenger Announcement System</Title>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="A" repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" opsIndicator="(O)">
<Title>Alternate Procedures Used</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided alternate procedures are established and used.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationProcedure>
<Para>Alternate procedures:</Para>
<Para>The Pilot-in-Command must brief cabin crew members that the prerecorded announcements are affected and announcements must be made by cabin crew member when required.</Para>
<Para>Cabin crew members must ensure that necessary demonstration equipments are available on-board.</Para>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="B" repairInterval="D" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0">
<Title>Procedures Do Not Require Its Use</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided procedures do not require its use.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
</DispatchCondition>
